{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-fable-5","id":"msg_011Cd7EKNKsKkJ42THV5zwvs","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01MUYRu5d98zfR2sKyaa5531","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/tmp/arena-ws.52i0sm/REPORT.md","content":"## Overview\n\nBetween May 2 and May 21, 2026, the company recorded 30 orders with total revenue of $7,154.44. The median order value was $204.94. Sales spanned four products (Widget, Gadget, Sprocket, Doohickey) and four regions (North, South, East, West).\n\n## Top Products\n\nGadget led all products with $2,392.00 in revenue from just 16 units, thanks to its $149.50 price point. Widget followed at $2,118.94 on 106 units, appearing in more orders than any other product. Doohickey earned $1,513.00 from 17 units, while Sprocket ranked last with $1,130.50 despite moving 238 units — by far the highest volume — at only $4.75 each.\n\n## Regional Performance\n\nNorth was the strongest region at $2,176.35, driven by steady Widget volume and two Gadget orders. East followed with $1,830.79 and South with $1,732.48. West trailed at $1,414.82, the only region below $1,500, with lower unit counts across most of its orders.\n\n## Recommendations\n\n- Gadget generated $2,392.00 from only 16 units; prioritize Gadget marketing, since each additional sale adds $149.50 in revenue.\n- Sprocket sold 238 units yet earned just $1,130.50; consider raising its $4.75 price or bundling it with higher-margin products.\n- West trails all regions at $1,414.82, roughly 35% below North's $2,176.35; target West with focused sales attention.\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1154,"cache_read_input_tokens":23536,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1154,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":67,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"global"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"paren